{"tid":1404777,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警狗水平發射擊破攝記面罩","createTime":"2019-08-04T06:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:32:01.000Z","uid":43231,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"253bdc481322eb2cbcab902b0f99e636865e6105","tid":1404777,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:01:42.000Z","msg":"昨晚警方在尖沙咀警署附近、龍堡國際對出發射第一輪催淚彈，一反以往習慣、向天發射，而是呈水平向人群橫射。首輪發射四枚催淚彈均直射本媒攝影師Kaiser，其面罩被擊中後破裂，面部感到震動，幸好人並無受傷。唯其後所攝的照片是在裝備不齊全下完成。<br />\n<br />\n圖1:有關口罩破裂，有催淚彈從罩的右下角朝左上擦過痕跡。<br />\n<br />\n圖2:事發時本媒記者拍得的相片。<br />\n<br />\n圖3:防暴警察呈水平向人群直射催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n攝：Kaiser @ USP United Social Press 社媒<br />\n#USP20190803TST<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7KQaWQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7KQaWQ.png&h=69921fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWsY4gR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWsY4gR.png&h=e14ca22e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"091dd41dfc8ce76cb58a09efab7ce5312fcd73ee","tid":1404777,"uid":43231,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:02:28.000Z","msg":"水平發射催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8229d3e9a9030d194ee8907e7b4315eab0706368","tid":1404777,"uid":43231,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"冇面罩個攝記分分鐘爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067a6a96b549015b2498aa62819a6ba5c0d20ab3","tid":1404777,"uid":57771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:07:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87adbe1705e9ba31654a5d5677ae2424f0f31e88","tid":1404777,"uid":49853,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:07:40.000Z","msg":"冇得射實彈,所以將催淚彈當實彈射"},{"pid":"e035feff2c99fde543394fcafa0d9065e3fcd717","tid":1404777,"uid":43231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:09:13.000Z","msg":"大家唔好對警暴麻木<im